      "udi": "umb://element/b66d3cf8fe1944b8b6aba3e2e3fed447",
      "title": "Programme details",
      "content": "<p>Title : BA (Hons) Business Management</p>\n<p><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://scqf.org.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Scottish Credit and Qualifications Framework\">SCQF Level</a> : 10</p>\n<p>Mode of delivery : Face-to-face with some hybrid learning</p>\n<p>Duration : normally 4 years</p>\n<p>Language of delivery : Greek</p>"
    },
